"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-Divine-ascents-Church-s-climbing-wall-draws-new-crowd-at-Paris-2024-1vXlhoi1mJG-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Ken Browne in Paris  Copied  They turned a chapel in central Paris into a climbing center, and it's packed full of the faithful.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cClimbing District, the company behind this, runs urban climbing walls and with the sport featuring at the Olympics, business is booming.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"We are standing in an old chapel dating back to the middle of the 19th century which was converted into a climbing wall in November 2022 when we went through seven months of works,\\\" Antoine, the co-founder of Climbing District, told CGTN.  \\\"We have got a 13m high wall and we welcome roughly 300 people every day.\\\"  Following the sport's debut at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, climbing's popularity has soared around the world.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cKelly is a new member of climbing's congregation.  \\\"It's a great place to make friends and friends that have the same passion as you so that's just awesome,\\\" she said.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cWorld Health Organization (WHO) figures show that one in four adults do not meet recommended levels of physical activity worldwide, and in France almost half of women and 30 percent of men are physically inactive.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThe city of Paris is trying to use the Games to encourage people to get moving, and with climbing, once you start you can not stop, says Kelly.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"Even when I do not climb I think about it, when I eat, when I sleep I think about this one\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 I do not know, I think about it all the time.\\\"  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIn the Olympic spirit, it was time for this journalist to get involved,WATCH the video above to see how I got on.  Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"